    "chemicalDescription": [
      "Tripeptide-46 Hexapeptide-40 Decapeptide-27 Methionyl Oligopeptide-91 Tetrapeptide-38 sh-Oligopeptide-1 is a single chain synthetic fusion peptide, produced by fermentation in  E. coli.  The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from Tripeptide-46, Hexapeptide-40, Decapeptide-27, Oligopeptide-91, Tetrapeptide-38 , sh-Oligopeptide-1 with the initiation code for Methionine. The fusion peptide contains a maximum of 98 amino acids and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
